These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, tea, water
7 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, mah-jongg, chess, billiard, domino, bridge
There 7 different types of food: pear, pomegranate, pepper, lettuce, strawberry, onion, apricot
 1. the person drinking water is the person playing domino##1
 2. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 5. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person eating pomegranate is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person playing chess is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
11. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
12. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
13. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
14. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
16. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
17. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
18. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
19. the person eating pomegranate is the person drinking tea##1
20. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | tea        | 7up       | lemonade | milk     |
| Game   | domino   | bridge       | mah-jongg  | canasta  | chess  | backgammon   | billiard  |
| Food         | apricot | strawberry         | onion  | pomegranate | pear | lettuce  | pepper |

